OL,6,F"This is why it is important that you
OL,7,Funderstand the partnership's actions
OL,8,Fprior to Alfie's murder, and the
OL,9,Fmeasures put in place to ensure
OL,10,Fchildren are listened to and kept
OL,11,Fsafe.J"In the immediate aftermath of
OL,12,FAlfie's murder, we carried out an
OL,13,Finitial review of West Mercia Police's
OL,14,Finvolvement with the family. As a
OL,15,Fdirect result, enhanced training has
OL,16,Fbeen put in place for our front-line
OL,17,Fofficers and staff to ensure they
OL,18,Ffully understand the signs of
OL,19,Fvulnerability, that they are
OL,20,Fprofessionally curious and don't take
OL,21,Finformation on face value. We've also
OL,22,Fworked to ensure that our officers and
OL,23,Fstaff are aware of and consider
OL,24,Falternative measures available to us
OL,25,Falongside criminal proceedings, such
OL,26,Fas civil orders.
