OL,6,F"After Alfie's case had been heard in
OL,7,Fcourt, we made a referral to the
OL,8,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,9,Fto ensure independent assessment of
OL,10,Four contact with the family. This
OL,11,Finvestigation remains ongoing, but we
OL,12,Fhave committed that the findings will
OL,13,Fbe shared with you as soon as they can.
OL,15,F"We fully support the recommendations
OL,16,Fof the review and are absolutely
OL,17,Fcommitted to working within the
OL,18,Fpartnership to continually develop and
OL,19,Fimprove safeguarding measures for
OL,20,Fvulnerable children and young people."
